<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_528_r1l3">
<add><expan>Erſame<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> vnd</add> <expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> Von der newikeit wegen des vnterkauffs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l4">cʒu frankfurt / als <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> auch wol <expan>vviſſentl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l5">iſt / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir den von frankfurt etvvieofft mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l6"><expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> potſchaft <expan>ſchrifftlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſüſt <expan>fleiſſıklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l7">ermant vnd bıten laſſen . ſölch newikeit . abcʒulaſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l8">des vvir doch biʒ her an Jn niht <expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mochten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l9">Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns vnſer kaufflewte wol vnter richtet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l10">daʒ ſölch newikeit / euch vnd den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> . vns vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l11">vnd auch dem gemeinen kauffman gar ſchedlıchen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l12">vnd <expan>vnübervvintlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd auch cʒemal niht cʒuleiden ſey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l13"><expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe damit in Jren <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>hantyrung<ex>en</ex></expan> in mancher = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l14">ley vveiſe vaſt beſweret werden . das Jn gar vnbequemlich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l15">iſt / darcʒu auch cʒubeſorgen ſeẏ . vvo dıeſelb newikeit alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l16">fürgang gevvünne . daʒ fürbaʒ mer newikeit dem kauffman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l17">dauon entſteen <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> . Hyrümb <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> deuht 
<del rend="strikethrough"> nu </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l18"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> fürſıchtikeit daʒ davvıder ichts cʒu erdenken oder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l19">cʒetun wer / damit ſölch newikeit <expan>abgetrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd fürbaʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l20">deſt mẏnder newikeit angefangen <expan>vvürd<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add>
<del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_528_line_1592203074119_2138">vnd daʒ man beẏ </ab><ab facs="#facs_528_line_1592203077186_2143"><expan>alte<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> blib </ab></del></add> So <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_line_1592203024934_2098">vvir gern vnſer erber potſchaft darümb cʒu den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l23">bıʒ gen Meincʒ ſchicken . ſich mit einander 
<del rend="strikethrough">etvvaʒ </del> dauon </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_line_1592203039106_2112">cʒu vnter reden 
<add><ab facs="#facs_528_line_1592203080936_2148">daʒ man beẏ <expan>alte<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_528_line_1592203084136_2153"> <expan>herkume<ex>n</ex></expan> blib </ab></add> vvas nü <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> vveiſheit darümb 
<del rend="strikethrough">alſo </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l26">cʒeſynne 
<add><ab facs="#facs_528_line_1592203041827_2117">well ſein </ab></add> . das lieſʒt vns bey den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> boten <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l27">vviſſen vnd auf vvelhe cʒeit So vvolten vvir darumb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_528_r1l28">dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> alſo hin abe ſenden / Vnd wo etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ın dıe Galli </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_528" id="263r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
